{"tid":2155731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被三警私刑虐待老翁早前判囚 提出刑期上訴得直 即時獲䆁","createTime":"2020-08-14T03:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T10:13:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":350,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"72e2f68d3ad3ea48da8c0cb2cdf6067363365344","tid":2155731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"62歲老翁鍾志華去年6月25日在上水因醉酒鬧事送院，懷疑遭三警私刑虐待，至於老翁亦承認毆打途人及警長。他早前承認襲警及普通襲擊兩罪後，被粉嶺法院裁判官蘇文隆重囚半年。他今向高等法院提出刑期上訴得直，即時獲䆁，法官彭寶琴押後頒布書面裁決理由。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人質疑原審裁判官使用考慮兩罪刑罰同期抑或分期執行時犯錯，至於兩名事主傷勢輕微，法庭毋須就襲警罪採納最高刑期，扣減認罪折扣後判處4月。上訴人又強調被告沒有酗酒習慣，也非有預謀犯案。<br />\n<br />\n法官彭寶琴同意，儘管法庭有須要保護執法者，但根據上訴庭指引，最高刑罰只適用於情節刞惡劣的案件，但本案被告只對警長揮拳一下，法庭沒有理由採納最高刑罰。"},{"pid":"8c24f8d4223e0b4a2f23c638ce51b74f6bd745ad","tid":2155731,"uid":21545,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"彭寶琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c904d40c514de0906c5d87cacf25b55d23364c","tid":2155731,"uid":187,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"彭寶琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513e33a35ce45f6dcfe1c1f70fbb601de3aa3449","tid":2155731,"uid":231583,"like":167,"dislike":0,"sco