e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"飲醉伸左一拳半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97988c9d221a947e4d6360e9cd3fe455ac702485","tid":2155731,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d81118d110bb7599d71e825045eff5e903681fee","tid":2155731,"uid":121961,"like":56,"dislike":11,"score":45,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>紅底法官竟然正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"因為個阿伯唔係因為政治入獄"},{"pid":"1da77948ab71638eb658bb27129ccbb1fabbd794","tid":2155731,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72e2f68d3ad3ea48da8c0cb2cdf6067363365344","tid":2155731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"62歲老翁鍾志華去年6月25日在上水因醉酒鬧事送院，懷疑遭三警私刑虐待，至於老翁亦承認毆打途人及警長。他早前承認襲警及普通襲擊兩罪後，被粉嶺法院裁判官蘇文隆重囚半年。他今向高等法院提出刑期上訴得直，即時獲䆁，法官彭寶琴押後頒布書面裁決理由。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人質疑原審裁判官使用考慮兩罪刑罰同期抑或分期執行時犯錯，至於兩名事主傷勢輕微，法庭毋須就襲警罪採納最高刑期，扣減認罪折扣後判處4月。上訴人又強調被告沒有酗酒習慣，也非有預謀犯案。<br />\n<br />\n法官彭寶琴同意，儘管法庭有須要保護執法者，但根據上訴庭指引，最高刑罰只適用於情節刞惡劣的案件，但本案被告只對警長揮拳一下，法庭沒有理由採納最高刑罰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"主審法官彭寶琴個人資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180518/N7E3O4KPZYFRMS7US7CWLSVS5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180518%2FN7E3O4KPZYFRMS7US7CWLSVS5M%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5dd16fe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180518%2FN7E3O4KPZYFRMS7US7CWLSVS5M%2F&h=76e15c1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180518/N7E3O4KPZYFRMS7US7CWLSVS5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥應該和彭寶琴是很好的朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LxjqJkVM2_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLxjqJkVM2_M&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a5d1c0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LxjqJkVM2_M</a><br />\n<br />\n高院法官彭寶琴將「梁天琦」和強姦犯相提並論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/697463/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/697463/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bb9eb9073bf65944da5230b383e285e9825d9749","tid":2155731,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"推 【反守為攻】國際線極缺錢眾籌要你支持！ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149416</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"622e47aa1a7ebfd5988513f6f936b23b2acb18d2","tid":2155731,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c9d65cac09d2282ee9e2170fe68ea73f796610f","tid":2155731,"uid":335434,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"d81118d110bb7599d71e825045eff5e903681fee","tid":2155731,"uid":121961,"like":56,"dislike":11,"score":45,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>紅底法官竟然正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"唔係彭寶琴正常 而係蘇文隆對非藍絲嘅判刑太撚癲姐 呢單判半年同社工調停判1年都係完全脫離晒法律原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57163f40b5a52ba324c3215bcba6ccf4aae741b3","tid":2155731,"uid":115662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df4f2b3e4c333f39403c76f3612f9d57e52310c","tid":2155731,"uid":155936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:21:09.000Z","msg":"如果無記錯尖沙咀個白衫女子用觀星筆被狗屈襲警係判3個月<br />\n呢單半年明顯過重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:48